name: Ossiam Shiller Barclays CAPE® US Sector Value TR UCITS ETF 1C (EUR Hedged)
description_en: The Ossiam Shiller Barclays CAPE® US Sector Value TR UCITS ETF 1C (EUR Hedged) seeks to track the Shiller Barclays CAPE® US Sector Value (EUR Hedged) index. The Shiller Barclays CAPE® US Sector Value (EUR Hedged) Strategy selects from the S&P 500 the five sectors with the lowest relative CAPE (Cyclically Adjusted Price Earnings). The relative CAPE coefficient evaluates the relative cost performance of a sector based on its current and long-term historical prices and returns. Then the method calculates the sector with the lowest price dynamics over a period of 12 months, i. e. the sector with the worst performance during the period under review. Each of the remaining four sectors receives the same weighting (25%) and the components of the investment universe are realigned monthly. Currency hedged to Euro (EUR).
